ine":31},{"w":"Christ","s":116.06,"e":116.46,"line":32},{"w":"took","s":116.46,"e":116.82,"line":32},{"w":"the","s":116.82,"e":117.98,"line":32},{"w":"void","s":117.98,"e":118.02,"line":32},{"w":"and","s":118.8,"e":119.14,"line":32},{"w":"made","s":119.14,"e":119.42,"line":32},{"w":"me","s":119.42,"e":120.5,"line":32},{"w":"whole.","s":120.5,"e":121.34,"line":32}],"lines":[{"s":0.06,"e":0.257,"text":"TITLE: INFINITE GOOD / 2I MONSTER"},{"s":0.257,"e":0.226,"text":"humble but colossal gospel trap sci-fi anthem, cinematic alien rap, “2I MONSTER” energy, summoning infinite power to do infinite good, not for ego, not for fame, not for control — only to serve, heal, feed, shelter, protect, uplift, and glorify Jesus Christ"},{"s":0.226,"e":0.221,"text":"128 BPM, G major / E minor"},{"s":0.221,"e":3.38,"text":"massive gospel choir, thunder 808s, crisp trap claps, dark cosmic synths, orchestral brass, angelic pads, arena-sized hook, jaw-dropping drop, futuristic holy war drums, emotional redemption build, clean radio-ready mix"},{"s":3.38,"e":3.68,"text":"Theme:"},{"s":4.52,"e":46.68,"text":"A hyper-intelligent gray alien comes from beyond the stars seeking ultimate power, but Christ teaches him the highest power is love without limit. He calls down infinite mercy, infinite wisdom, infinite resources, infinite courage, and infinite compassion — then pours it into the streets to do infinite good. He asks the poor what they need, then gives every advantage possible: food, shelter, phones, IDs, job links, clean clothes, rides, training, prayer, dignity, protection, and hope."},{"s":46.68,"e":47.187,"text":"Hook energy:"},{"s":47.44,"e":49.76,"text":"summon the light, let it flood through the hood"},{"s":50.22,"e":52.4,"text":"infinite power for infinite good"},{"s":52.92,"e":54.56,"text":"not for the crown, not misunderstood"},{"s":55.26,"e":57.76,"text":"2I MONSTER, but I’m serving like I should"},{"s":58.24,"e":60.32,"text":"big and bad, humble and lit"},{"s":60.72,"e":62.4,"text":"holy fire, never counterfeit"},{"s":63.34,"e":65.62,"text":"silly, stupid, cosmic, rad"},{"s":65.7,"e":68.4,"text":"best you had, now you been had"},{"s":68.4,"e":68.83,"text":"Mood:"},{"s":69.26,"e":75.944,"text":"humble, lit, massive, holy, cosmic, triumphant, funny, reverent, streetwise, explosive, redemptive, world-saving, gospel-supernova energy"},{"s":75.944,"e":75.96,"text":"Vocal style:"},{"s":75.96,"e":78.5,"text":"Lil Baby melodic trap bounce, NF emotional intensity, Chill Bump clever conscious rap, huge"},{"s":78.5,"e":80.84,"text":"But wisdom is kneeling,"},{"s":81.18,"e":83.56,"text":"And power is giving,"},{"s":84.46,"e":86.42,"text":"And Christ is the reason"},{"s":86.42,"e":89.02,"text":"The dying start living."},{"s":89.16,"e":92.24,"text":"I’m a gray alien, ancient and wise,"},{"s":92.64,"e":94.94,"text":"Ten thousand thoughts behind obsidian eyes."},{"s":94.96,"e":97.5,"text":"I crossed every galaxy looking for light,"},{"s":97.66,"e":100.08,"text":"Then found the universe kneeling to Christ."},{"s":100.16,"e":102.78,"text":"No empire, no crown, no throne in the sky,"},{"s":102.82,"e":105.42,"text":"Just mercy so deep it can teach stars to cry."},{"s":105.44,"e":108.04,"text":"From the mothership down to the streets at night,"},{"s":108.36,"e":110.7,"text":"Gray alien genius made whole by Christ."},{"s":112.02,"e":115.7,"text":"Gray mind, bright soul,"},{"s":116.06,"e":121.34,"text":"Christ took the void and made me whole."}],"duration":134.44,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.233Z","stats":{"whisperWords":245,"polishedWords":331,"matched":209,"matchRate":0.631}}